Text: Just another hog on Helvete is 8 seconds long. I've downloaded it twice, so the problem isn't at my en. Rather annoying! Anyone care to upload a complete Helvete (or just JAH)? It's one of my favourite albums and i want to hear all of it!
@ athelvete, whats the point? the band already split up so buying their music isnt gonna support them.
All mp3s are at 128kpbs, such a great band deserves better quality.
